ops::bit::BitOr::bitor.doc:
Performs the `|` operation.

# Examples

```
assert_eq!(true | false, true);
assert_eq!(false | false, false);
assert_eq!(5u8 | 1u8, 5);
assert_eq!(5u8 | 2u8, 7);
```

